{"tid":1385120,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"雲海：破例代商業機構發聲「Apple員工致香港」","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:38:38.000Z","uid":68632,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ff019534ebd3c9c61b33f339343fcac863341256","tid":1385120,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"致香港市民、Apple 擁戴者及Apple仝人/全體員工<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群Apple 香港員工，為香港的Apple用戶服務八年。我們喜歡這品牌，更熱愛香港。我們可以視而不見，聽而不聞，但我們不會，切肉不離皮，任何一個人有事等如我們有事，任何一個區被破壞等如我們的家園被破壞，香港，如果不是連成一體，那就不如不是香港。<br />\n<br />\n自六月起，連串反送中示威活動，一百萬人上街，二百萬零四人二度上街，政府無動於衷，依然固我，把香港人的訴求當頭皮碎屑撥入垃圾籮。香港正處於一個水深火熱的境地，我們沒有選擇。<br />\n<br />\n對示威者使用過度武力、選擇性執法，以及近日白衣暴徒無的放矢襲擊元朗市民，警方沒有及時制止和有效執法。有幾多無辜市民受傷，有幾多無辜市民被捕，犧牲自由與身體保衛香港，政治黑暗，施法不公，警黑勾結，政府罔顧市民生死，情況令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n我們只是一群Apple職員，我們不能在做些什麼，但我們亦要做些什麼。社會各界，包括公共運輸車長、專業界別及公務員紛紛作出聯署，我們亦義無反顧支持大家。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，我們都有一個夢想，希望追求一個自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<br />\nWe are here to enrich lives.&nbsp;<br />\nTo help dreamers become doers,&nbsp;<br />\nto help passion expand human potential,&nbsp;<br />\nto do the best work of our lives.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n這是Apple 告訴我們的社會價值，我們希望能協助夢想家變成實踐者。我們更希望將一個更美好的香港，留給下一代。所以以此拋磚引玉，希望更多同事和服務業的同仁能表態。令政府真正回應市民的訴求，不能讓施政一錯再錯。<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\nPeople who work to leave this world better than they found it. <br />\n我們想留給下一代更好的香港<br />\n<br />\n一群熱愛香港的藍精靈上<br />\n<br />\n有心人，可聯絡TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/backhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbackhk&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=8b7fb730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/backhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2906280776080704?s=1425849770&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F197517173623758%2Fposts%2F2906280776080704%3Fs%3D1425849770%26sfns%3Dmo&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmIwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=1fb0162c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/197517173623758/posts/2906280776080704?s=1425849770&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziOHQiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziOHQiM.png&h=a3efd830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WaE71q9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWaE71q9.png&h=ea7a36f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gNCJzL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgNCJzL9.png&h=b60d8d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHHmmra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHHmmra.png&h=27278577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇罷買"},{"pid":"496977c354c4189b80cccd86c57ba7a5fa375397","tid":1385120,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"外國勢力"},{"pid":"8f880d74926c6249dc8ab32d5ae46677c9e5680e","tid":1385120,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"罷工啦屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07686a72d1eea003ce4497c900289051c9e4890e","tid":1385120,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f880d74926c6249dc8ab32d5ae46677c9e5680e","tid":1385120,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"罷工啦屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"罷買先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e5318971d0c6a8d98c009c8cd884ff819924f4","tid":1385120,"uid":68632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"黑警請轉會"},{"pid":"73e5fbf3091ee6898a9b4ff8d27ef4515f4571f6","tid":1385120