-30T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"我見蘋果成日好多人入黎問野，都唔係幫襯。<br />\n有次聽到個阿叔大大聲講，開咁大間鋪，微訊都唔唔識整。個藍精靈都好細心咁講其實微訊唔係蘋果出。<br />\n各藍屍，其實幫緊你地既藍精靈都係反送中。<br />\n你地唔好「無事就廢青，有事搵藍精」<br />\n如果人地唔幫你，我會答你「人地都係打份工，有情緒的」"},{"pid":"8eddbcb62b84e660de075c0cb33aa4846ac2a6f0","tid":1385120,"uid":276471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"推到更多蘋果人爆料"},{"pid":"a94ceca6ddebc8b28cb02a3da1d6bf90abe882b6","tid":1385120,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd10330829c97febdee268c1424eb4899b40885","tid":1385120,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"串柒柒既藍精靈請一齊串柒港共"},{"pid":"ad5df1a15e097d37779cbcc07770878226fd5212","tid":1385120,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"687fde09182f7736b8fd403fe4cb94e811364be3","tid":1385120,"uid":276471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:13:52.000Z","msg":"記唔記得有前警察話，黑警未有方法破解iphone Face Lock"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"fbi都要搵以色列hacker嚟搞先掂<br />\n仲要講緊幾年前先得<br />\n香港黑警算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"ee39aaf33e94716c437d99d040e6e0b33a798ffa","tid":1385120,"uid":31166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母最大粒嗰個管理層<br />\n佢肯定會秋後算帳<br />\n佢同777一模一樣樣"},{"pid":"6a58f01ca8ee71e4626426df7efebdb80edd0b5d","tid":1385120,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"愛國愛黨，勿用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"}]}